  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à Akonadi</title>

    <para><application>Akonadi</application> is an extensible cross-desktop storage 
    service for PIM data et meta data providing concurrent read, write, et query 
    access. It will provide unique desktop wide object identification et retrieval.</para>

    &lfs67_checked;

